🏠 1st Place: A $300 gift card to the @bloomsupps website + a year subscription to @theslayapp + a $100 Target gift card 
🏠 2nd Place: A $100 gift card to @bloomsupps website + a year subscription to @theslayapp 
-
Winners will be announced on my story Wednesday 7/21 at 5PM PST! Go go go!! 🎉🎁
